\id PHP  
\h Aj Filipos 
\toc3 Fil. 
\toc2 Aj Filipos 
\toc1 Tuꞌj Pabl kye Nimil aj Filipos 
\mt1 Tuꞌj Pabl kye Nimil aj Filipos 
\ip At jun chꞌuq nimil kubꞌ xkye tuꞌn Pabl toj tnam Filipos tojjo tkabꞌ tbꞌe te qꞌmal Tyol Dios (\xt Kybꞌi. 16:12-40\xt*). Te tzuybꞌil teꞌ uꞌj luꞌn, o yolin Pabl tiꞌj ttzaljbꞌil ex tkꞌuꞌjbꞌil ex jun chjonte te Dios kyiꞌjjo nimil toj Filipos. Ex ikyxjo, juntl tumil tiꞌjjo uꞌj luꞌn nxi tqꞌoꞌn chjonte kye nimil tiꞌjjo jun onbꞌil tzaj kysmaꞌn te, teꞌ tkuxtaq toj tze (\xt 4:18\xt*). Tzmataq ntzꞌibꞌin Pabl, kubꞌ t-ximin tuꞌn t-xi tqꞌoꞌn junjun xnaqꞌtzbꞌil kye nimil, a kꞌuꞌjlinqetaq tuꞌn antza. 
\ip Tojjo tuꞌj, nyolin Pabl tiꞌj jun tzaljbꞌil exla qa toj yajbꞌil, quꞌn exla qa tkuꞌxtaq toj tze, me nyolin Pabl toj uꞌj luꞌn tukꞌa nim yol te tzaljbꞌil, a tzajnin tiꞌjjo tnukꞌbꞌil qMan Dios toj tanmin. Ex nyoliꞌn uꞌj lo tiꞌj qa il tiꞌj tuꞌn qmutxsin qibꞌ tzeꞌnku te Crist (\xt 2:6-11\xt*). Ikyxjo, nyolin tiꞌj oxe tten Dios. Ntzaj tkujsin Pabl tojjo tuꞌj, qa ate Manbꞌaj tukꞌax Kꞌwalbꞌaj noq junx Dios, ex atzin kꞌulbꞌil noq okx te kyeku tuꞌn t-xiꞌye. Ex tzeꞌnku tuꞌn t-xi tqꞌmaꞌn tiꞌj Crist, a qAjaw, nkubꞌ tyekꞌin Pabl tiꞌj Jesucrist qa ax Diosjo kye aj Israel. Ex ikyxjo, nkubꞌ tyekꞌin qa ikyx te Xewbꞌaj Xjan mujle tten tukꞌa Manbꞌaj (\xt 3:3\xt*) ex tukꞌa Jesucrist (\xt 1:19\xt*). 
\ip Ex nyolin tiꞌjjo t-xtalbꞌil qMan Dios tuꞌn qklet. Atzin jaꞌlin, ajo kychwinqil nimil, noq tuꞌn kyanqꞌin tzeꞌnku ntqꞌmaꞌn Tbꞌanil Tqanil. Ex atziꞌn qmujbꞌil qibꞌ tukꞌa Crist atzin ttxuyil qkꞌuꞌjbꞌil qibꞌjo tuꞌn qajbꞌin kye txqantl. 
\c 1  
\s1 Jun qꞌolbꞌil kye nimil toj tnam Filipos 
\p  
\v 1 Ayiꞌn Pabl, nxi ntzꞌibꞌinjiꞌy uꞌj luꞌn junx tukꞌa wukꞌiy, Timotey. Awoꞌy taqꞌnil Crist, a Jesús, ex nxi qtzꞌibꞌiꞌn te kyeꞌy, kykyaqila nimilqiꞌy, junx kyukꞌa aye nejinel ex aye mojil kyxola, ayiꞌy Ttanim qMan Diosqiꞌy toj tnam te Filipos,\x + \xo 1:1\xt Kybꞌi. 16:12.\x* ex at kymujbꞌil kyibꞌa tukꞌa Jesús, a skꞌoꞌnxix tuꞌn qMan Dios te Klolqe.  
\v 2 Axit qMan Dios ex qAjaw Jesucrist kyꞌiwlil kyeꞌy tukꞌa tkyaqil tnukꞌbꞌil ex t-xtalbꞌil kyibꞌaja. 
\s1 Nnaꞌn Pabl Dios kyiꞌj nimil 
\p  
\v 3 Tkyaqil maj tzeꞌnku nchi ul julkꞌaja toj nkꞌuꞌja, bꞌeꞌx nxi nqꞌoꞌn chjonte te qMan Dios kyiꞌja.  
\v 4 Ex ikyxjo a tzeꞌnku nchin aqꞌiy naꞌl Dios, majx nxi nqaniꞌn tukꞌa tzaljbꞌil jun kyꞌiwbꞌil kyibꞌaja.  
\v 5 Ikytziꞌn, ma tzikyꞌx quꞌn junx kyukꞌiy, noq tuꞌn tqꞌmet Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, toj tnejil qꞌij tej kynimiꞌn, ex tzmax tzaluꞌn.  
\v 6 Qꞌuqle nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌj qMan Dios, a kubꞌ xikyꞌbꞌinte aqꞌuntl lo toj kyanmiꞌn; ex ax nbꞌinchin teꞌ nimxixl aqꞌuntl te tzꞌaqtzbꞌilte kyeꞌy,\x + \xo 1:6\xt Sal. 138:8.\x* tzmax ajxi tul Jesucrist juntl majl.  
\v 7 Tojxix tumil jun nxima ikyjo kyiꞌja kykyaqila, quꞌn tzunxix nqꞌaqꞌin nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja wen, quꞌn ikyx kyejiꞌy tkyꞌiwbꞌil Dios kyukꞌa tzeꞌnku wukꞌiy, iꞌchaqtzin intinkutz wetza toj tze, mope qa ma chin pon kaniꞌn kywutz kawil, noq oꞌkx tuꞌn nkoliꞌn wen tiꞌj Tyol Dios, ex tuꞌn nqꞌmantiꞌy qa twutzxixjo anetziꞌn.  
\v 8 Quꞌn ate Dios ojtzqil weꞌy, qa nimxix tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja kykyaqila, noq tuꞌn tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil tkꞌuꞌj Jesucrist toj wanmiꞌn.  
\v 9 Ex nchin qaniꞌn toj nnaꞌj Diosa kyiꞌja, tuꞌn tten nimxixl tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja kyxolxa, ex tuꞌn tten kynabꞌla, ex tuꞌn tel kynikyꞌa te tkyaqil,  
\v 10 tuꞌntzin tbꞌantjo a tbꞌanilx wen. Ikytzin kbꞌantile tsaqix kychwinqiljiꞌy wen, tuꞌntzin aj tul Crist, ntiꞌtla jun kyila kknetil.  
\v 11 Ikytzin kchi okilejiꞌy tzeꞌnku twutz qawal tbꞌanilx tuꞌn tonbꞌil Jesucrist, tuꞌnjo kybꞌinchbꞌiꞌn tbꞌanilx toj tkyaqil. Ayetzin kybꞌinchbꞌiꞌn, nchi ajbꞌin te aqꞌbꞌil chjonte, ex te nimsbꞌil tbꞌi qMan Dios kyuꞌn txqantl. 
\s1 Nimxixtl toklin Jesucrist tibꞌaj tkyaqil toj tchwinqil Pabl 
\p  
\v 12 Werman, waja tuꞌn kybꞌintiꞌy qa tkyaqiljo ma tzikyꞌx wiꞌja, ma tzꞌajbꞌin tuꞌn t-xi laqꞌe Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil,  
\v 13 ex tuꞌn kybꞌiꞌnte jniꞌ aj kawil kyukꞌaꞌ kyaqꞌnil toj ja te kawbꞌil, ikyqexjo xjal tojile tnam. Kykyaqilxjo luꞌn, ma kybꞌi, ex ma tzꞌel kynikyꞌ, qa noq tuꞌnjo nchin ajbꞌin te qꞌmal te Tbꞌanil Tqanil tiꞌj Crist, ma chin kutz kyqꞌoꞌn toj tze.\x + \xo 1:13\xt Kybꞌi. 28:30.\x* 
\v 14 Ex noq tej kylonte jun chꞌuq erman, teꞌ nkux qꞌoꞌn toj tze tuꞌn tpaj nchin yolintaqa tiꞌj tbꞌi Jesús, bꞌeꞌx jaw kyiꞌn kyibꞌ, ex el kyxobꞌil kyiꞌj tuꞌn tqꞌmetjo Tbꞌanil Tqanil, noq tuꞌnjo qꞌuqlexix kykꞌuꞌj tiꞌj Jesucrist, a tAjaw Tkyaqil. 
\p  
\v 15 Nya ikyjo tzeꞌnqekuꞌ tojjo juntl chꞌuq, a nchi qꞌman tqanil Crist, me tukꞌa ikyꞌbꞌil wiꞌja, ex nloꞌchj kyanmin tuꞌn qꞌoj. Me metzin kyeꞌ a tnejil chꞌuq nchi qꞌumlaj kyeꞌ toj tumil tukꞌa tkyaqil kyanmin.  
\v 16-17 Ayetzin kyeꞌ tkabꞌ chꞌuq, a nchi qꞌman tqanil Jesús tukꞌa qꞌoj, nya jikyin iteꞌ toj kynimbꞌil, ex nkubꞌ kybꞌisin tuꞌn tok nimxixl bꞌis wiꞌja, tuꞌn intinkutza toj tze. Me atzin tnejil chꞌuq, nchi yolin kyeꞌ tqanil Crist toj tumil, ex tukꞌa tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil kykꞌuꞌj tiꞌj qMan Dios; ikytzin bꞌin kyuꞌn, qa noq tuꞌn nchin kolintaqa tiꞌj Tbꞌanil Tqanil Jesucrist, intinkutza tzaluꞌn toj tze. 
\p  
\v 18 Nya weꞌ te, quꞌn exla qa jikyinqe wen toj kynimbꞌil mo ex qa minaj, noqtzin tuꞌn a wejiꞌy nchin tzalaj tiꞌj, tuꞌn loqe nchi yolin tiꞌj Tbꞌanil Tqanil tiꞌj Crist. 
\p  
\v 19 Ikytziꞌn, qꞌuqle nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌj kynaꞌj Diosa wiꞌja, ex ikyxjo tiꞌj Xewbꞌaj Xjan, ax T-xew Jesús, lu nmojin wiꞌja tuꞌn njaxa tzaluꞌn toj tze.  
\v 20 Ex te Dios nxi nqaniꞌn, tuꞌn ntiꞌtla jun nkyꞌiy toj nchwinqila, tuꞌn njaw tzꞌaqa toj nnimbꞌila, ex tuꞌn njaw txꞌixwiꞌy tuꞌn; qalaꞌ tukꞌa nimxixl wipiꞌn, tuꞌn nyoliꞌn tiꞌj kolbꞌil tukꞌa qꞌuqbꞌil nkꞌuꞌja. A jaꞌlin ex kukxitlaꞌ, chin yolinjiꞌy tiꞌj, tuꞌntzin tqꞌanchaꞌlix nimsbꞌil tbꞌi Crist toj nchwinqila tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, ex ajxi nkyima.  
\v 21 Quꞌn toj nchwinqila tzaluꞌn, ntiꞌ juntl tbꞌanilx tzeꞌn Crist;\x + \xo 1:21\xt Gal. 2:20; Col. 3:4.\x* ex aj nkyima, nimxla tzaljbꞌil, quꞌn kchin tenbꞌila tukꞌa te jun majx. 
\p  
\v 22 Qa atx toj nqꞌija tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, ok chin ajbꞌilx weꞌ toj taqꞌin qAjaw. ¿Me tzeꞌntzila k-okile aqꞌuntltz qa ma chin kyima? Ntiꞌ n-el nnikyꞌa tuꞌn ikyjo.  
\v 23 At kabꞌe tumil: Tnejil, qa wenxixtla te weꞌy tuꞌn nkyima, tuꞌntzin nteꞌn tukꞌa Crist, quꞌn axixtla wajiꞌy.  
\v 24-25 Me atzin tkabꞌ tumil: Noq tuꞌn kypaja, wenxitla te weꞌy tuꞌn nteꞌn chꞌintla twutz txꞌotxꞌ, tuꞌn nmojiꞌn te qꞌol tumil kyeꞌy, ex tuꞌn tten nimx tzaljbꞌil toj kynimbꞌila. Me ikytzin qꞌuqle nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌjjo luꞌn, tuꞌn ttzaj tqꞌoꞌn chꞌintl toj nqꞌija, tuꞌntzintla nteꞌn chꞌintla kyxola.  
\v 26 Tuꞌntzin ikyjo, chin ajbꞌila juntl majla kyxola te qꞌuqbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja, noq tuꞌn tbꞌi Crist, a Jesús. 
\p  
\v 27 Oꞌkx jun tumiljo nxi nqꞌoꞌn kyeꞌy: Kyqꞌoꞌnka tilil, tuꞌn tten kychwinqila, ikyxixjo tzeꞌnku ntzaj tyekꞌin Tbꞌanil Tqanil Crist. Exla qa intiꞌn kyukꞌiy exla qa mina, quꞌn tuꞌn najchaq intiniꞌy kykꞌatza; me atla wajiꞌy, noq tuꞌn tul jun kyqanila, qa tbꞌanilx iteꞌyiꞌy, ex qa jikyin iteꞌyiꞌy toj kychwinqila, ex qa at kymujbꞌil kyibꞌa kyxolilixa kykyaqila, ex qa nchi aqꞌniꞌn wen toj kynimbꞌila, a tzaj qꞌoꞌn kyeꞌy, tej kynimiꞌn Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil,  
\v 28 tuꞌntzintla mi tzaje kyxobꞌila kye kyajqꞌoja, ex tuꞌntzintlaꞌ kyteꞌn ikyjo, k-elile kynikyꞌ kyiꞌja, qa kyjaꞌ kyxiꞌ toj najin, ex ikyx n-ajbꞌineꞌ te yekꞌbꞌil, qa ma chi klet kyeꞌ tuꞌn Dios.  
\v 29 Ikytziꞌn, noq tuꞌn ma chi kleta tuꞌn Crist, at kyokliꞌn jaꞌlin, nya noq oꞌkxjo tuꞌn kynimiꞌn tiꞌj, qalaꞌ ikyxjo, tuꞌn tikyꞌx kyuꞌn noq tuꞌn tpaj tbꞌi.  
\v 30 Ikytziꞌn, ayiꞌy ex ayiꞌn junx n-ikyꞌx quꞌn, ex tok tilil taqꞌin qMan Dios quꞌn.\x + \xo 1:30\xt Kybꞌi. 16:19-40.\x* Ma tzꞌok kykaꞌyiꞌn ojtxe qa ma tzikyꞌx wuꞌn, teꞌ s-ok tilil aqꞌuntl wuꞌn. Ex n-ok kybꞌiꞌn jaꞌlin, qa tzunx n-ikyꞌx wuꞌn, tuꞌn tzunx nchin aqꞌninxa toj taqꞌin qMan, ex luꞌn tok tilil wuꞌn. 
\c 2  
\s1 Qo ok tzeꞌnku te Jesucrist 
\p  
\v 1 Atzin jaꞌlin, qatzin qa twutzxix qa a Crist nqꞌonte ambꞌil kyeꞌy, tuꞌn tjaw kyin kyibꞌa; ex qa at-xix qꞌuqbꞌil kꞌuꞌjbꞌaj kyukꞌiy; ex qa at Xewbꞌaj Xjan kyxola; ex qa kyojtzqiꞌnxixa tsoꞌjbꞌajil Jesús, ex qa at tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil tkꞌuꞌj kyukꞌiy; qa twutzxix kykyaqiljo luꞌn,  
\v 2 kyqꞌonktzintza jun kytzaljbꞌila weꞌy, tuꞌn kyyekꞌin kyibꞌa, tuꞌntla junx tuꞌn tbꞌete kynabꞌla, ex junx tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja, ex tukꞌa junxchꞌin kyumila ex junxchꞌin kyajbꞌila.  
\v 3 Mit kubꞌ kybꞌinchiꞌn jun tiꞌ noq tuꞌnjo at tajbꞌin kyeꞌy, ex nya tukꞌa kynimsbꞌil kyibꞌa, qalaꞌ tukꞌa kymutxbꞌil kyibꞌa teyile junjun, ex tuꞌn kyximiꞌn kyiꞌjjo txqantl, qa nimxixtl kyoklin toj taqꞌin qMan Dios.  
\v 4 Mix aꞌl jun kyeꞌ, tuꞌn tkubꞌ tbꞌinchin jun tiꞌ, noq tuꞌn tknetjo a te teku, qalaꞌ noq tuꞌn tel wenku te tkyaqilx. 
\p  
\v 5 Junxit tel kyximbꞌitza kykyaqila, ikyxjo tzeꞌnku te Crist, a Jesús;  
\v 6 quꞌn ikyx t-xilin luꞌn: 
\q1 Me exla qa ax Diosjo,\x + \xo 2:6\xt Jn. 1:1-3; Col. 1:15, 19; 2:9.\x* 
\q2 me mix jaw tiꞌne tibꞌ, tuꞌn tok toklin tzeꞌn te Dios, 
\q1  
\v 7 qalatziꞌn, bꞌeꞌx xkyij ttzaqpiꞌn toklin toj kyaꞌj, 
\q2 exsin s-ok tqꞌoꞌn tibꞌtz tzeꞌnkuj jun kyaqꞌnilxjal.\x + \xo 2:7\xt Jn. 1:14.\x* 
\q1  
\v 8 Atzaj teꞌ s-ok te xjal, 
\q2 xkubꞌtzin tyekꞌin tmutxbꞌil tibꞌ,\x + \xo 2:8\xt 2Co. 8:9.\x* 
\q2 ex kubꞌ tnimin tMan, 
\q2 ex xi tqꞌoꞌn tibꞌ tuꞌn tkyim twutzjo cruz;\x + \xo 2:8\xt Mt. 26:39; Jn. 10:18; Eb. 5:8.\x* 
\q2 ikytzin s-ele kyiꞌn xjaljo ttxꞌixew, nyakuj tzeꞌn jun aj il. 
\q1  
\v 9 Tuꞌn xkubꞌ tnimintz ikyjo, ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Dios nimxix toklin, 
\q1 ex ma tzꞌok qꞌoꞌn te tAjaw Tkyaqil, 
\q2 tukꞌa nimxixtl toklin tibꞌaj tkyaqilx.\x + \xo 2:9\xt Eb. 2:9; 12:2.\x* 
\q1  
\v 10 Tunpetziꞌn, bꞌin quꞌn, qa nimxix toklin tbꞌi Jesús. 
\q1 Ex tuꞌn ikyjo, noq twutz, kchi kꞌwele mejeye kꞌulil, a iteꞌ toj kyaꞌj, ikyqexjo a iteꞌ twutz txꞌotxꞌ, ex ikyqexjo tkyaqil kyimnin. 
\q1  
\v 11 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, tkyaqilx tuꞌn tkubꞌ nabꞌlinte, ex tuꞌn tkubꞌ qꞌmante, 
\q1 qa oꞌkx Jesucrist, a tAjaw Tkyaqil, ok te nimsbꞌilte tbꞌi qMan Dios.\x + \xo 2:11\xt Is. 45:23.\x* 
\s1 Awotzinqe a nimilqo, tuꞌn qok te jun yekꞌbꞌil kywutz nya nimil 
\p  
\v 12 Atzin jaꞌlin, werman, ex nimx nqꞌaqꞌin nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja; ikytziꞌn tzeꞌnkuj in kubꞌ kynimiꞌn, tej nteꞌn kyukꞌiy, exsintla nimxixtl tuꞌn nkubꞌ kynimiꞌn jaꞌlin, a najchaq intiniꞌy kykꞌatza. Quꞌn tuꞌnjo ma chi kleta, kyqꞌonktzin tilil, tuꞌn tkubꞌ kyniminjiꞌy kolbꞌil kyeꞌy, me tukꞌa kymutxbꞌil kyibꞌa, ex tuꞌn tten tchewil qMan Dios kyiꞌja.  
\v 13 Ikytziꞌn, ate Dios ktzajil qꞌonte tumil tiꞌjjo wen, a kyaja, ex ktzajil qꞌonte mojbꞌil kyeꞌy, tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo lo kyuꞌn, tzeꞌnku taj qMan Dios. 
\p  
\v 14 Kybꞌinchinkutziꞌn tkyaqilx tukꞌa tkyaqil kykꞌuꞌja, ex nya tuꞌn kyjaw chꞌotje, ex nya tuꞌn kyjaw yolbꞌiꞌn,  
\v 15 tuꞌntzin ntiꞌ kyila kywutzxjal, a nya nimilqe ex bꞌinchil ilqe. Qalaꞌ chi okxita tkꞌwal qMan Dios, ex ntiꞌtla kytzꞌilila toj kychwinqila. Qalaꞌ chi okxa tzꞌaqle wen, tzeꞌnqe cheꞌw nchi qoptzꞌaje toj qnikyꞌin; ex ikyxqetzintla kyejiꞌy tukꞌaꞌ kybꞌinchbꞌin toj kynimbꞌila kyxoljo nya nimil, a toj qxopin iteꞌye,\x + \xo 2:15\xt Deu. 32:5.\x* 
\v 16 tuꞌntzin tjaw kynimsiꞌn toklin Tbꞌanil Tqanil tiꞌjjo saq chwinqil. Ikytziꞌn, aj tul Crist, ok knaꞌbꞌilx wejiꞌy tzaljbꞌil wen kyiꞌja, aj tok nkaꞌyiꞌn qa nya noqx kukxjo in aqꞌniꞌn kyxola, ex nya noqx kukxjo ma tzikyꞌx wuꞌn tuꞌn tpajjo in yoliꞌn tqanil kolbꞌil kyeꞌy.  
\v 17 Exla qa ma chin kyima tzaluꞌn toj tze noq tuꞌn kypaja, a noq tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo kynimbꞌila, a jun oyaj xi kyqꞌoꞌn twutz qMan Dios; ex ok kchin tzalajila ikyjo, tuꞌntzintla qtzalaj junx kyukꞌiy toj qnimbꞌil.  
\v 18 Nya tuꞌn ikyjo, qa ma chin kyima, chi kꞌwela numjiꞌy, qalaꞌ chi tzeꞌjexixa tzeꞌnku weꞌ. 
\s1 Kabꞌe tbꞌanil nimil: Timotey ex Epafrodito 
\p  
\v 19 Atzin jaꞌlin, qa iky tajbꞌil qAjaw Jesús, nchin ximin tuꞌn t-xi smet Timotey liweyku te lol kyeꞌy. Ex qa bꞌaꞌn iteꞌyiꞌy, ikytzin k-ajbꞌile kyqaniljiꞌy te jun tzaljbꞌil te weꞌy.  
\v 20 Ikytzin mix aꞌl juntl nximin kyiꞌja tzeꞌn te Timotey. Ikyx t-ximjo kyiꞌja tzeꞌnku weꞌ nxim, quꞌn tok tilil tuꞌn, tuꞌn tonin kyukꞌiy.  
\v 21 Qalatzin kyeꞌ txqantl, noq te kyex kyeꞌ nchi ximin, ex nchi aqꞌnin; me atzin tiꞌjjo te Crist, a Jesús, mina nkubꞌ kyximin taqꞌin.  
\v 22 Me ikytzin bꞌin kyeꞌ kyuꞌn, ex ojtzqiꞌn kyeꞌ kyuꞌn, qa tzun n-aqꞌnin Timotey; ex tukꞌa tkyaqil tajbꞌil n-aqꞌnin wukꞌiy, tuꞌn tqꞌmet Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, iky tzeꞌnku jun kꞌwal n-ajbꞌin te ttata.  
\v 23 Tunpetziꞌn, ax kxel nchqꞌoꞌn te lol kyeꞌy, ex k-okil kybꞌiꞌn te, tzeꞌn intiniꞌy toj nchwinqila ex toj taqꞌin qAjaw Jesús.  
\v 24 Me qꞌuqle weꞌ nkꞌuꞌj tiꞌj qAjaw, tuꞌn njatza tzaluꞌn toj tze, ex loqinl weꞌ, liweyku chin poꞌn lol kyeꞌy. 
\p  
\v 25 Ex il tiꞌj tuꞌn taj nchqꞌoꞌn a erman Epafrodito, axj ten te mojil wukꞌiy toj aqꞌuntl, ex n-ikyꞌx yajbꞌil tuꞌn junx wukꞌiy, tuꞌn tqꞌmetjo Tyol Dios. Ex axjo erman, tzaj kychqꞌoꞌn te lolte weꞌy, tuꞌn tok bꞌinchit jun tiꞌ weꞌy.  
\v 26 Nkubꞌ t-ximin tuꞌn t-xiꞌ lol kyeꞌy kykyaqila, ex tuꞌn tpon tqanil kyeꞌy, tuꞌnjo chꞌime xkyime, teꞌ xyabꞌte, quꞌn ma kybꞌiꞌy qa ma yabꞌte.  
\v 27 Twutzx teꞌ, ma kubꞌ yabꞌte tetz, ex chꞌintlx mi xkyime. Bꞌaꞌnpetzin ma qꞌaqꞌin tkꞌuꞌj qMan Dios tiꞌj, ex nya noq oꞌkx tiꞌjkuꞌ erman, ex ikyxjo weꞌ, tuꞌn mi tzaje juntl bꞌis wiꞌja tibꞌajxiljo bꞌis tok wiꞌja tzaluꞌn toj tze.  
\v 28 Tuꞌntzintzjo, il tiꞌj tuꞌn t-xi nchqꞌoꞌn kykꞌatza tuꞌntzin tok kykaꞌyin twutz, ex tuꞌn kyjaw tzalaja, aj kylontiꞌy. Ex ikyx wejiꞌy, tuꞌn mi chin bꞌisintla tiꞌj kyqanila.  
\v 29 Kykꞌmonxa tukꞌa tkyaqil kytzaljbꞌila, tzeꞌnkux jun erman, a wenxix tiꞌj qAjaw Jesús, ex kynimsinqeksjiꞌy kykyaqil nimil, a ikyx tumiljo kyuꞌn tzeꞌnku erman lo.  
\v 30 Quꞌn, chjonte Dios, mi xkyim te erman tzaluꞌn, teꞌ attaq nkꞌatza, noq tuꞌn tpajjo n-ajbꞌin te Crist. Chꞌime xkyije tchwinqil noq tuꞌn tpajjo n-ajbꞌin weꞌy te kyxeljo, tuꞌntaq kymojin wukꞌiy. 
\c 3  
\s1 Nya tuꞌn qbꞌinchbꞌin aku qo klete 
\p  
\v 1 Atzin jaꞌlin, werman, chi tzalajxa tuꞌn kymujbꞌil kyibꞌa tukꞌa Jesús, a tAjaw Tkyaqil. Te weꞌy, ntiꞌ tkyꞌi tuꞌn t-xi nnaꞌnjiꞌy a o kyij ntzꞌibꞌiꞌn; ikytzin nim tajbꞌin te kyeꞌy:  
\v 2 Kykaꞌyink kyibꞌa kye xjal, a nya bꞌaꞌn nbꞌant kyuꞌn, a nya toj ttxolil nxaꞌye kynabꞌl. Noq kyaj tuꞌn tok kyqitin jun techil tiꞌj ttzꞌumil kychibꞌjila, tuꞌn kyoka te kye, ex tuꞌn kybꞌinchiꞌn jun tiꞌ tibꞌaj kynimbꞌila tiꞌj qAjaw Jesús.  
\v 3 Qalatziꞌn qe, awoxixqe at qechil tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, a awo nqo kꞌulin twutz qMan Dios. Ex tuꞌn ikyjo, nqo tzalaj tuꞌn ma qo ok te Crist, a Jesús, jaꞌlin, ex nya tuꞌn jun techil tiꞌj ttzꞌumil qchibꞌjil,\x + \xo 3:3\xt Jer. 4:4; Ro. 2:28-29; Gal. 6:14-15; Col. 2:11-13.\x* quꞌn nya tuꞌn qbꞌinchbꞌin kqebꞌile qkꞌuꞌj te kolbꞌilqe.  
\v 4 Noqpetzin iky tetz, ayintla weꞌ tnejil tuꞌn tok qe nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌj nbꞌinchbꞌiꞌn.  
\v 5 Quꞌn wajxaq qꞌijtaq witzꞌjliꞌn, tej tok qitit wechila tiꞌj nchibꞌjila, tuꞌn tyajil Israelqiꞌn; tzajninqiꞌn tojjo jun chꞌuq xjal, a tyajil Benjamín.\x + \xo 3:5\xt Ro. 11:1.\x* Judiyqiꞌn, ex Judiy ntatiꞌy. Ex qa tiꞌjjo tumil kykawbꞌil Judiy, ojtzqiꞌnjo lo wuꞌn, quꞌn jun Pariseyqintaqa.\x + \xo 3:5\xt Kybꞌi. 23:6; 26:5.\x* 
\v 6 Ex qꞌiꞌnxixtaq wibꞌa tuꞌn kykubꞌjo nimil wuꞌn.\x + \xo 3:6\xt Kybꞌi. 8:3; 22:4; 26:9-11.\x* Ex tuꞌn tkubꞌ bꞌinchitjo tkawbꞌil Moisés, mixtaq aꞌl juntl aku tzaj qꞌmaꞌnte jun tyol wiꞌja ex weꞌy. 
\p  
\v 7 Tkyaqilxjo a anetziꞌn, tbꞌanilxtaq te weꞌy. Me atzin jaꞌlin, ntiꞌl tajbꞌin te weꞌy, quꞌn tuꞌn o chin nimin tiꞌj Crist.  
\v 8 Quꞌn, qa ma tzꞌok nmujbꞌin nchwinqila jaꞌlin tukꞌa ojtxe, ntiꞌx tajbꞌin nchwinqila ojtxe tzeꞌnku jaꞌlin, a ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Crist, a Jesús. Tuꞌntzintzjo, tkyaqiljo a ojtxe, ma kyij nnajsin jaꞌlin, ex ma kyij nqꞌoꞌn tzeꞌnku tzꞌis, quꞌn tuꞌn tbꞌanilxix juntl nchwinqila o tzaj tqꞌoꞌn wAjawiꞌy, a Jesucrist.  
\v 9 Ex tzunx nchin tzalajxa, quꞌn tuꞌn junx nmujbꞌil wibꞌa, ex nchin bꞌeta junx tukꞌa. Nya waja txi nqꞌmaꞌn, qa tuꞌn nnimbꞌila tiꞌj tkawbꞌil Moisés, najsite wila; qalaꞌ ikytziꞌn, noq tuꞌn nnimbꞌila tiꞌj Crist. Ex tuꞌnxjo nnimbꞌila tiꞌj Crist, in kletiꞌy tuꞌn.  
\v 10 Ex tuꞌntzintzjo, waja tuꞌn wojtzqiꞌntejiꞌy tajbꞌil qAjaw, ex tuꞌntzintla nnaꞌntejiꞌy tipin Jesús toj nchwinqila, a tipin ikyx tzeꞌnku tej tjatz itzꞌje juntl majl kyxol kyimnin. Ex ikyxjo, waja tuꞌn tikyꞌx wuꞌn, tzeꞌnku ma tzikyꞌx tuꞌn, ex tzmaxi aj nkyima.\x + \xo 3:10\xt Gal. 4:19.\x* Ikytziꞌn, waja tuꞌn tjapin bꞌaj nnimbꞌila tzeꞌn tjapin bꞌaj tuꞌn qAjaw, tej tkyim.  
\v 11 Ex atzin jaꞌlin, at jun qꞌuqbꞌil nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌj jun tkabꞌ chwinqil, a tbꞌanilx wen, aj kyjatz anqꞌin kyimnin. 
\s1 Tok tilil quꞌn tuꞌn qkanbꞌin teꞌ a o tzaj ttziyin qMan Dios 
\p  
\v 12 Me ikytziꞌn, nya tuꞌnjo ma txi nqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy, matzintla japin bꞌaj tkyaqil wuꞌn, ex matzintla chin oktza tzꞌaqle. Qalaꞌ ikytzin atzin lajoꞌnxjo wuꞌn, ex qꞌuqlek nkꞌuꞌja tiꞌj, tuꞌntzin tjapin bꞌantjo luꞌntz. Quꞌn tuꞌnpen tpaj teꞌ, ẍin tzaje ttxkoꞌne weꞌ Crist, a Jesús, tej nkleta tuꞌn.  
\v 13 Werman, ayinxi nchinx qꞌmante kyeꞌy, nya mat japin tzqetjo luꞌn wuꞌn, a tuꞌnjo nxi nqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy. Qalatzin weꞌ tuꞌn tkubꞌ nbꞌinchin ikyjo kyjaluꞌn: Tuꞌn tkyij nnajsinjiꞌy a tkyaqiljo ma kyij wiꞌjxiꞌy, ex tuꞌn t-xi wiꞌn wibꞌa kujxix wen, tuꞌntzin tjapin bꞌaj wuꞌn a naꞌmx kyul kanin,  
\v 14 ex tuꞌntzin nkaniꞌn tojjo a lajoꞌnx wuꞌn, ex tuꞌn tkanbꞌitjo a oyaj toj kyaꞌj, qꞌoꞌntz tuꞌn qMan Dios, atxix tej xqo ttxok, tuꞌn qmujbꞌin te qibꞌ tukꞌa Crist, a Jesús. 
\p  
\v 15 Qkyaqilx a ma qo kujix toj qnimbꞌil, atzin qeꞌ tuꞌn tkubꞌ qbꞌise. Me meqa mikyxil kyeꞌ kyxim, ax Dios kqꞌolte tumil kyeꞌy,  
\v 16 quꞌn il teꞌ luꞌn tiꞌj, tuꞌn tkubꞌ qximin, a ma tzꞌel qnikyꞌ te, ex tuꞌn tkubꞌ bꞌinchit. 
\p  
\v 17 Ayiꞌy werman, chi lipektziꞌn wiꞌja, ex tiꞌjjo a nxi nqꞌmaꞌn,\x + \xo 3:17\xt 1Co. 4:16; 11:1.\x* ex kykaꞌyinktziꞌn kyiꞌjjo aye iky nchi bꞌete tzeꞌnku a o txi qxnaqꞌtziꞌn kyeꞌy.  
\v 18 Tuꞌntziꞌn ikyjo, ilaꞌx maj, o txi nqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy, ex jaꞌlin nxi nqꞌmaꞌn juntl majla tukꞌa taꞌl nwutza, quꞌn tuꞌn at ilaꞌ nchi bꞌet nyakuj ajqꞌojqe tiꞌj tcruz Crist, quꞌn nkyqꞌmaꞌn qa nya noq oꞌkx tuꞌn tkyimlin Jesús at kolbꞌil, qalaꞌ il tiꞌj tuꞌn qqitin qechil tiꞌj ttzꞌumil qchibꞌjil tuꞌn qklet, chi chiꞌ.  
\v 19 Toj najin chi xeꞌle kye xjal anetziꞌn, quꞌn atzin kyachbꞌil nya wen ma tzꞌok te kydios, ex atziꞌn kytzaljbꞌil ikyjo, bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn kytzaj txꞌixwe tuꞌn. Ex oꞌkx nchi ximin kyiꞌjjo kykyaqil nya bꞌaꞌn te twutz txꞌotxꞌ. 
\p  
\v 20 Me metzinqe qtanim, a jaꞌ qo tenbꞌile, antza taꞌya teꞌ toj kyaꞌj, a jaꞌ ktzajila juntl majl Jesús, a Crist ex tAjaw Tkyaqil, a nqo ayoꞌn tiꞌj.  
\v 21 Atzin kjawil txꞌixpinte qxmililjo, a qꞌiꞌntaq quꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ tzaluꞌn, tuꞌn tok tzeꞌnku t-xmilil Jesús toj kyaꞌj, a tbꞌanilx wen. Ex nya oꞌkx kbꞌantiljo tuꞌn Jesús, qalaꞌ okpe kbꞌantil tetz tuꞌn, tuꞌn tokx tkyaqil tjaqꞌ tkawbꞌil, tuꞌnxjo tipin. 
\c 4  
\s1 Kukx qo tzalaj toj tkyaqil noq tiꞌj tbꞌi qAjaw 
\p  
\v 1 Tuꞌntzintzjo, ayeqiꞌy werman, a nimxix nqꞌaqꞌin nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja, nim waja tuꞌn nlon kyeꞌy. Ikytziꞌn ayeqiꞌy ntzaljbꞌila ex yekꞌbꞌil teꞌ twutz waqꞌnbꞌiꞌn. Mitzin tzꞌel kytxalpin kyibꞌa toj kynimbꞌila tiꞌj tAjaw Tkyaqil, qalaꞌ kyinxsinjiꞌy kyteꞌn ikyjo a jikyin wen. 
\p  
\v 2 Atzin jaꞌlin, chin kubꞌsil nwutza kyeꞌ erman qya, a Evodia tukꞌa Síntique, noq tuꞌn tkubꞌ kyxmoxin kyibꞌ wen kyxolx, ex tuꞌn tok kymujbꞌin kyibꞌ toj kynimbꞌil ex toj taqꞌin qAjaw, a Klolqe te jun majx.  
\v 3 Ex ikyx te tey, chin kubꞌsil nwutza, a ay wukꞌaxixa toj aqꞌuntl, tuꞌn tmojin kyukꞌaxjo qya luꞌn; ikytziꞌn, ma chi aqꞌnin kyeꞌ qya lo kuj wen junx wukꞌiy, tuꞌn tqꞌmet Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, junx tukꞌa erman Clement, ex kyukꞌa txqantl erman. Quꞌn ikytzin o kyij tzꞌibꞌin kybꞌi teyile junjun toj tuꞌjil chwinqil te jun majx. 
\p  
\v 4 Tuꞌntzintzjo, chi tzalajxa wen tiꞌj tbꞌi qAjaw toj tkyaqil. Kxel nqꞌmaꞌn juntl majla kyeꞌy. Kukx chi tzalajxa wen toj tkyaqilx,\x + \xo 4:4\xt Neh. 8:10; 1Tes. 5:16.\x* 
\v 5 tuꞌntzin kylonte kykyaqilxjal, qa nimilqiꞌy, noq tuꞌn kychwinqila tbꞌanilx wen. Quꞌn ikytzin nqatzx tuꞌn tul qAjaw Jesús. 
\p  
\v 6 Ex mina chi ja labꞌtiꞌy tiꞌj jun tiꞌ, qalaꞌ kyqꞌmaꞌnxa nej twutz qMan Dios toj kynaꞌj Diosa. Ex kyqꞌoꞌma chjonte, ex kyqaninxa tukꞌa kynimbꞌila.\x + \xo 4:6\xt Col. 4:2-4; 1Tes. 5:17-18.\x* 
\v 7 Tuꞌn ikyjo, tzul jun tnukꞌbꞌil Dios kyeꞌy, a nimxixtl tzeꞌnku n-el kynikyꞌxjal te. Ex atzin nukꞌbꞌil kꞌuꞌlte kyanmiꞌn ex kynabꞌla te nya wen, quꞌn mujleqiꞌy tukꞌa Crist, a Jesús. 
\s1 Qo ximin tiꞌj tkyaqil wen 
\p  
\v 8 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn werman, chi ximinqiꞌy tiꞌj tkyaqiljo a twutzx, ex tiꞌj tkyaqiljo a at tajbꞌin, ex tiꞌj tkyaqiljo jikyin taꞌye, ex tiꞌj tkyaqiljo a tzꞌaqlexix, ex tiꞌj tkyaqiljo wen, ex tiꞌj tkyaqiljo at tokin twutz qMan Dios. Atzin kyejiꞌy kyximbꞌitz, quꞌn tuꞌntzin wen kyyol xjaltz kyiꞌja, ex okpela kꞌwel kynimsin tbꞌi Dios tuꞌn ikyjo. 
\p  
\v 9 Kybꞌinchinkutzinjiꞌy a o bꞌaj nyekꞌiꞌn, ex o txi nxnaqꞌtziꞌn kyeꞌy, ex n-ok kybꞌiꞌn, tzeꞌn nxi nqꞌmaꞌn, ex o tzꞌok kykaꞌyiꞌn toj nbꞌinchbꞌiꞌn. Atzin kybꞌinchinkujiꞌy, ex atzin qMan Diosjo, a tAjaw tkyaqil nukꞌbꞌil, ktenbꞌil kyukꞌiy toj tkyaqil. 
\s1 Jun oyaj te Pabl kyuꞌn aj Filipos 
\p  
\v 10 Nim nchin tzalaja wen, noq tiꞌj tbꞌi qAjaw, tuꞌnjo ma chin tzaj kynaꞌn juntl majla, tuꞌn ttzaj kysmaꞌn jun onbꞌil jaꞌlin. Ex nya noq otaq chin el naje toj kykꞌuꞌja, qalaꞌ naꞌmtaq tbꞌanttaq tuꞌn kyyekꞌintejiꞌy kyxima luꞌn.  
\v 11 Ex nya tuꞌnjo atit ma tzꞌel bꞌaj weꞌy, qalaꞌ naqꞌleqin weꞌ, aj qa at, ex tzeꞌnku ntiꞌ. Ikyx nchin tzalaj wejiꞌy, qa at ex tzeꞌnku ntiꞌ.  
\v 12 Naqꞌleqin weꞌ, tuꞌn wanqꞌin toj yajil ex qa toj qꞌinimil. O chin naqꞌet weꞌ toj tkyaqiljo ntzaj wiꞌja: Qa nojninqiꞌn, mo qa at waꞌyaj wiꞌja; ex qa at maj mina nbꞌaj wuꞌn, ex atku maj qa ntiꞌpeltz.  
\v 13 Tkyaqilx weꞌ aku tzikyꞌx wuꞌn, quꞌn ate Crist nmojin weꞌy.  
\v 14 Me ikytziꞌn, ex wen teꞌ xbꞌant kyuꞌn, tej ẍin tzaj kyoniꞌn toj tkyaqiljo n-ikyꞌx wuꞌn. 
\p  
\v 15 Ex ojtzqiꞌn kyuꞌn ayeqiꞌy aj Filipos, teꞌ tzaj xkye nqꞌmantiꞌy Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil toj Macedonia, ex tzmax tzaluꞌn, ex oꞌkqex kyeꞌ ma chi onin weꞌy. Me mix aꞌl juntl Ttanim Dios ma tzꞌonin wiꞌja tiꞌjjo onbꞌil, a xi nqꞌoꞌn kyeꞌy, a Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil.  
\v 16 Ex ikyxjo, tej nteꞌn toj tnam Tesalónica,\x + \xo 4:16\xt Kybꞌi. 17:1.\x* ma tzaj kysmaꞌn ilaꞌ maj kyonbꞌila, tzeꞌnku atxtaq taj wey.\x + \xo 4:16\xt 2Co. 11:9.\x* 
\v 17 Ex jaꞌlin, nya noq tuꞌn njyoꞌn tiꞌj jniꞌ onbꞌil te weꞌy, qalaꞌ wajatlaꞌy tuꞌn kyel wena twutz qMan Dios toj qꞌij te paꞌbꞌin.  
\v 18 Ex ma tzul toj nqꞌobꞌa tkyaqil onbꞌil kyuꞌn. Ex ma nintz weꞌ at we jaꞌlin, tuꞌnjo sul kaninjo kyonbꞌila tzaj kysmaꞌn tiꞌj Epafrodito. Atziꞌn onbꞌil, a saj kysmaꞌn, ma tzꞌok tzeꞌnku jun oyaj twutz qMan Dios, a manyor tbꞌanilx, tzeꞌnku tkꞌokꞌjil storak, aj tkubꞌ patit.\x + \xo 4:18\xt Ex. 29:18; 30:36-37.\x* 
\v 19 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, ate qMan Dios, a jaꞌ nchin ajbꞌiniꞌy, ktzajil qꞌoꞌnte tkyaqiljo atx taj kyeꞌy, a tzeꞌnkuxjo tbꞌanilxix tqꞌinimil toj kyaꞌj, noq tuꞌn Crist, a Jesús.  
\v 20 Tuꞌn tkyaqiljo luꞌn, njaw nimsit tbꞌi qMan Dios te jun majx. Ikyxit bꞌantjo. 
\s1 Jun qꞌolbꞌil kye nimil tuꞌn Pabl, noq tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo tuꞌj lo 
\p  
\v 21-22 Kyqꞌolbꞌinqexa toj nbꞌiꞌy kykyaqil nimil tiꞌj Crist, a Jesús. Ex ikyqex ermanjo, a iteꞌ wukꞌiy tzaluꞌn toj Rom, junx kyukꞌa tkyaqil erman nchi aqꞌnin toj ja te tkawbꞌil César, a nmaq kawil, nxi kyqꞌoꞌn jun qꞌolbꞌil kyeꞌy. 
\p  
\v 23 Noqit ax qAjaw Jesucrist tzaj qꞌoꞌnte t-xtalbꞌil kyibꞌaja kykyaqila.